observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Municipality undertake the following measures:

Perform periodic reconciliation of stock/property cards to ensure that discrepancies are immediately investigated, cleared and reconciled with the books of accounts;

Submit only the correct schedule for each account. Submission of two or more schedule casts doubt on the reliability of the report; and

Prepare necessary journal entries to adjust the duly investigated reconciling items in order to reflect the correct account balances;

